Valfaris is a 2D action platforming game developed by Steel Mantis and published by Big Sugar. 
The game was released for Windows and Nintendo Switch on October 10, 2019, and later for 
PlayStation 4 and Xbox One in November.
 Merge Games distributed the physical copies of the PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch versions in November 2019.
 Amazon Luna version arrived in December 2020. 
The game's soundtrack was composed by former Celtic Frost guitarist Curt Victor Bryant. 